- CLI `report_phase_outcome` fallback: `tanren-cli methodology --phase audit-task --spec-id <spec_uuid> --spec-folder <spec_dir> phase outcome --json '{"schema_version":"1.0.0","spec_id":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","outcome":{"outcome":"complete","summary":"phase complete"}}'`

